<function>

access:   public

name: fetch

param: string, $base

param: string, $class, NULL

return: array

</function>

Gets the class-to-file map for a class hierarchy.

* Parameters:

 * string //$base//: The path to the top of the class hierarchy, typically the base PEAR directory.

 * string //$class//: Start mapping with this class.

* Returns array: The class-to-file mappings.